snippet.title: yourstreetserenade
snippet.description:
I don't vid much anymore, but every once and awhile the fangirl in me will fixate on something so much that I'll be forced to (otherwise my brain gets all tingly). But I'm just happy to sit, watch, comment and squee about everyone else's work.


Favorite TV Shows: The X Files, Queer as Folk, Sons of Anarchy, The Walking Dead, Angel, Buffy, Nip/Tuck, 30 Rock, Arrested Development, Misfits, Dexter, Lost

Music: I listen to a lot of junk pop when I'm working out but I'm seriously passionate about...Radiohead, Stars, Garbage, Aimee Mann, Kathleen Edwards, Tegan and Sara, Geographer
